@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qfgsas(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (0.81 * wp.sin((tmp + 0.97 * v2 + 0.75)))
    v2 = wp.sin((tmp * (v2 + 0.77 + tmp + 0.84)))
    v1 = wp.cos((wp.cos(v1 + 0.66) - v0))
    v2 = 0.89
    data[tid] = v0
